room_title: Escape room "Wild West Saloon" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
room_description: The wildest cowboy in town, Jim “The Shooter” Williams, has been robbed of his prized gold. He is convinced that you have stolen his loot and locked you in Gem’s Saloon to round up the rest of his gang and come back for revenge. Can you figure out who stole Jim’s gold and escape in time?
